- Seo Yoon!
- Mom!

00:03:15.460 --> 00:03:17.440
Seo Yoon.

00:03:19.090 --> 00:03:22.120
Yes, you should stay there.

00:03:24.930 --> 00:03:28.950
I caught a cold.

00:03:28.950 --> 00:03:32.070
I guess you came here with the police officer Unni.

00:03:33.670 --> 00:03:35.110
Does it hurt a lot?

00:03:35.110 --> 00:03:37.560
No, just a little.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:41.740
But since you mustn't catch it...

00:03:41.740 --> 00:03:45.430
- I heard you're getting the surgery.
- Yes.

00:03:45.430 --> 00:03:48.960
You can't get sick before the surgery. Okay?

00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:51.780
Get through the surgery well,

00:03:51.780 --> 00:03:56.040
and do what Unni tells you to, okay?

00:03:56.040 --> 00:04:00.400
So that the three of us can get healthy and meet again.

00:04:03.310 --> 00:04:07.930
Seo Yoon, you should listen to your mom.

00:04:10.390 --> 00:04:12.890
I'll see you after your surgery.

00:04:12.890 --> 00:04:17.150
Mom... bye.

