[Final Episode]

00:05:46.100 --> 00:05:49.210
You don't need to be nervous over my questions.

00:05:49.210 --> 00:05:50.570
Okay.

00:05:50.570 --> 00:05:53.910
How many peopke are infected inside the building?

00:05:54.670 --> 00:06:00.760
If Detective Jung Yi Hyun is infected, too, then two people.

00:06:00.760 --> 00:06:04.290
Since there was someone named Na Soo Min on the 4th floor.

00:06:04.290 --> 00:06:08.250
And there are two more people who died after getting infected, right?

00:06:09.040 --> 00:06:13.020
Please tell me everything you know about the infected.

00:06:13.020 --> 00:06:16.020
We may need the information to develop a treatment.

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:23.780
Get through the surgery well. I'll come and visit you at the hospital with Ahjussi Jung Yi Hyun.

00:06:23.780 --> 00:06:26.680
My mom is infected, right?

00:06:26.680 --> 00:06:29.650
But she's just sick.

00:06:29.650 --> 00:06:31.720
Like me.

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:39.050
That's right. That's why she'll be all better.

00:06:39.050 --> 00:06:41.440
You and your mom, both of you.

00:06:57.370 --> 00:06:59.600
About Seo Yoon's mother...

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:05.060
She held out this long just to see her daughter. She won't be able to hold out anymore.

00:07:06.690 --> 00:07:11.150
She will be moved to the freezer warehouse in a day or two.

00:07:31.680 --> 00:07:34.550
We made this with your blood.

00:07:40.610 --> 00:07:44.580
Your antibody count is decreasing.

00:07:45.920 --> 00:07:49.620
- And?
- This is the last effective treatment available.

00:07:49.620 --> 00:07:55.560
We need to amplify it and use it for research in order to develop treatments.

00:08:02.050 --> 00:08:07.520
Then all you have to do is give it up for everyone's sake.

00:08:14.720 --> 00:08:18.560
A medical commander has come to take you.

00:08:18.560 --> 00:08:23.840
He wants to take you and the cure to the lab.

00:08:25.800 --> 00:08:31.000
So... are you breaking your promise?

00:09:14.970 --> 00:09:18.540
What are you doing? Stop him!

00:09:20.860 --> 00:09:22.920
It won't take long.

00:09:25.220 --> 00:09:28.250
Do you realize what you're doing?

00:09:29.800 --> 00:09:31.540
Of course, I do.

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:03.540
I'm done.

00:10:12.250 --> 00:10:15.460
Where's Yoon Sae Bom and the leftover cure?

00:10:15.460 --> 00:10:19.060
She just left. Didn't you see her?

00:10:32.390 --> 00:10:35.520
If you go out the back gate on the first floor, you'll see a car.

00:10:35.520 --> 00:10:38.920
I left you a present inside, so make sure to take it with you.

00:10:40.680 --> 00:10:42.420
Should you be doing this?

00:10:42.420 --> 00:10:46.760
I thought you were a very ambitious person.

00:10:46.760 --> 00:10:50.670
I have a plan, so don't worry. Just do what needs to be done.

00:10:50.670 --> 00:10:55.150
But if you get caught, there's nothing I can do for you.

