00:12:03.920 --> 00:12:05.860
Don't worry.

00:12:06.490 --> 00:12:08.620
You'll get better.

00:12:16.790 --> 00:12:19.070
What are you doing right now?

00:12:19.850 --> 00:12:22.160
That's the cure, right?

00:12:22.160 --> 00:12:24.010
Yes.

00:12:24.010 --> 00:12:27.910
I was going to leave, but I just couldn't.

00:12:31.950 --> 00:12:33.890
Do you want to shoot me?

00:12:39.910 --> 00:12:42.100
What are you going to do now?

00:12:42.100 --> 00:12:47.000
Even if you escape... you used up the cure.

00:12:49.930 --> 00:12:52.240
I'm not that special.

00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:56.830
There will be others with antibodies.

00:12:57.630 --> 00:13:03.690
Yi Hyun has me, but Seo Yoon... doesn't have anyone.

00:13:04.420 --> 00:13:09.040
Until then, I just need to stay by Yi Hyun's side.

00:13:11.580 --> 00:13:16.070
[General Service Center]

00:13:56.050 --> 00:13:59.250
Hurry and leave. They check people who are wearing protective gear.

00:13:59.250 --> 00:14:02.170
None will pay close attention to you.

00:14:03.800 --> 00:14:08.510
I always knew we had a connection.

00:14:11.730 --> 00:14:16.880
Hold on! You can't just leave.

00:14:19.890 --> 00:14:25.850
No, not that. People will get suspicious if I look fine.

00:14:26.520 --> 00:14:31.010
Really? But it'll hurt a lot.

00:14:31.960 --> 00:14:35.400
Hurry and do it before I change my mind.

00:14:39.360 --> 00:14:41.630
Close your eyes and take a deep breath.

00:14:47.400 --> 00:14:50.280
Wait! Not the face!

00:14:50.280 --> 00:14:52.650
Hit me someplace that won't hurt.

00:14:52.650 --> 00:14:54.560
People will get suspicious.

00:14:54.560 --> 00:14:58.510
Plus, the swelling on the face goes down the fastest.

00:14:59.220 --> 00:15:01.120
Okay.

00:15:01.810 --> 00:15:03.420
In one go.

00:15:34.010 --> 00:15:36.310
[Access Authorization]

00:15:36.310 --> 00:15:38.710
Thanks for the gift.

00:15:45.120 --> 00:15:48.080
[Student Dormitories]

00:16:00.200 --> 00:16:03.000
Did Yoon Sae Bom escape?

00:16:03.000 --> 00:16:06.660
You know getting fired won't be all, right?

00:16:06.660 --> 00:16:10.460
Why? Are you going to sentence me to death?

00:16:11.610 --> 00:16:14.650
I thought you were a smart punk.

00:16:15.410 --> 00:16:17.530
Why did you do it?

00:16:17.530 --> 00:16:22.510
If you had used the last cure on your wife, I could have let it go.

00:16:25.540 --> 00:16:29.530
I've done all kinds of things to lower the number of the infected.

00:16:29.530 --> 00:16:34.080
Lockdown, quarantine, killing...

00:16:36.580 --> 00:16:39.410
I have plenty of blood on my hands.

00:16:40.530 --> 00:16:44.850
Thanks to that, you succeeded and protected a lot of people.

00:16:44.850 --> 00:16:48.360
I only saw people as measures of efficiency and numbers.

00:16:49.540 --> 00:16:56.000
But after seeing Yoon Sae Bom, I realized that there are other ways.

00:17:40.950 --> 00:17:42.620
Hyun.

00:17:53.570 --> 00:17:58.450
When you were next to me, I didn't realize how precious you were to me.

00:18:00.520 --> 00:18:03.570
I will come get you, no matter where you are.

00:18:13.910 --> 00:18:16.290
I heard Yoon Sae Bom left wearing your uniform.

00:18:16.290 --> 00:18:21.210
- Yes, she forcibly—
- Never mind!

00:18:21.210 --> 00:18:23.020
Where do you think she went?

00:18:23.020 --> 00:18:26.990
It seems like she's planning to run away abroad with the cure.

00:18:26.990 --> 00:18:30.930
I think we should put out an APB in airports and ports.

00:18:31.660 --> 00:18:34.490
She probably went to her apartment since her husband is there.

00:18:34.490 --> 00:18:36.620
Sir.

00:18:37.690 --> 00:18:39.930
Keep going.

00:18:39.930 --> 00:18:42.970
There's an antibody carrier in that apartment building.

00:18:49.420 --> 00:18:52.140
Give me full authority.

00:18:52.140 --> 00:18:54.560
Then I will bring the person to you.

00:18:55.460 --> 00:18:56.930
Do you really think it's okay to leave?

00:18:56.930 --> 00:18:59.800
It's okay. You saw the news. Everything is fine outside.

00:18:59.800 --> 00:19:02.490
Everyone from Unit 501 left except the detective.

00:19:02.490 --> 00:19:04.310
Still, if we leave, too, it'll be—

00:19:04.310 --> 00:19:08.590
It's better if we're not here. We'll be helping by leaving.

00:19:09.560 --> 00:19:11.190
Oh?

00:19:12.060 --> 00:19:14.980
- Wait!
- Who is that?

00:19:17.250 --> 00:19:21.490
Oh! Hey, Unit 501! The wife in Unit 501!

00:19:21.490 --> 00:19:24.780
Hey, hurry and unlock this!

00:19:27.520 --> 00:19:29.880
Are you okay? Did you get hurt?

00:19:29.880 --> 00:19:32.620
- Did they tell you to come back in?
- Hold on.

00:19:32.620 --> 00:19:36.340
Where's Yi Hyun? Is he okay?

00:19:41.250 --> 00:19:43.480
Is he alive?

00:19:49.200 --> 00:19:51.370
[1 Day Before]

00:21:52.500 --> 00:21:56.700
Hyun, wake up.

00:21:58.040 --> 00:22:00.560
We have to see each other again.

00:22:09.430 --> 00:22:11.250
Sae Bom.

00:22:13.770 --> 00:22:16.510
Ahjussi, are you okay?

00:22:16.510 --> 00:22:19.550
You're bleeding a lot.

00:22:20.560 --> 00:22:22.680
I'm okay.

00:22:22.680 --> 00:22:24.890
I'll sleep a little bit.

00:22:26.220 --> 00:22:27.980
Okay...

00:22:45.270 --> 00:22:47.800
You're sure about this, right?

00:22:47.800 --> 00:22:50.630
You said it looks right, too.

00:22:50.630 --> 00:22:54.860
Oppa, I told you it's over if we get it wrong ten times!

00:22:54.860 --> 00:22:58.290
We need to consider all the possibilities.

00:23:08.310 --> 00:23:10.320
Who is it?

00:23:12.660 --> 00:23:16.480
Please help us. Please call the doctor.

00:23:16.480 --> 00:23:18.540
My husband got stabbed.

00:23:18.540 --> 00:23:22.490
He's conscious, but I think he lost a lot of blood. Please...

00:23:23.600 --> 00:23:25.660
Oh Joo Hyung really isn't here.

00:23:25.660 --> 00:23:28.880
I beg you. We're sorry for everything. Please.

00:23:28.880 --> 00:23:32.000
I said the doctor isn't here!

00:23:32.000 --> 00:23:33.810
Oppa, say something!

00:23:33.810 --> 00:23:35.520
Really, no one else is here.

00:23:35.520 --> 00:23:37.460
- Doctor!
- Come on!

00:23:38.940 --> 00:23:41.640
- Open the door! Open the door!
- But who...

00:23:41.640 --> 00:23:43.350
did that to him?

00:23:49.620 --> 00:23:52.620
- Damn it!
- Please open the door!

00:23:52.620 --> 00:23:54.900
Open the door! Open up!

00:23:55.620 --> 00:23:58.650
Do you think you'll survive after everyone else dies?

00:23:58.650 --> 00:24:01.570
I will set your unit on fire!

00:24:05.890 --> 00:24:08.050
Darn it.

00:24:15.140 --> 00:24:17.470
Open it!

00:24:30.460 --> 00:24:33.060
D-Doctor?

00:24:37.530 --> 00:24:39.760
Are you okay?

00:24:56.660 --> 00:24:59.020
Hey, you saw that, too, right?

00:24:59.020 --> 00:25:03.760
He was shot in the arm and the leg, but the bleeding has already stopped.

00:25:03.760 --> 00:25:07.240
That's a good thing. What's the problem?

00:25:07.240 --> 00:25:10.600
The smell of his blood disgusts me,

00:25:10.600 --> 00:25:14.560
and I don't want it. He's infected.

00:25:14.560 --> 00:25:17.370
What about my blood then? Did you want mine?

00:25:17.370 --> 00:25:21.570
Can you just listen to me and not change the subject? I'm saying he's infected!

00:25:21.570 --> 00:25:24.100
I don't hear you denying it.

00:25:24.100 --> 00:25:28.000
How could you want your sister's blood? What kind of brother are you?

00:25:28.000 --> 00:25:29.860
Oh...

00:25:29.860 --> 00:25:32.050
Oh, are you okay?

00:25:32.050 --> 00:25:35.050
- Get some water.
- Okay.

00:25:39.410 --> 00:25:42.240
What are you two doing here?

00:25:42.240 --> 00:25:48.160
You kept bleeding, and there was nothing I could do by myself.

00:25:49.440 --> 00:25:53.190
I put that on him in case he had an attack.

00:26:00.520 --> 00:26:01.950
Don't you feel thirsty?

00:26:01.950 --> 00:26:03.850
It's not as bad these days.

00:26:03.850 --> 00:26:05.830
I do feel thirsty

00:26:05.830 --> 00:26:10.090
but diabetes runs in our family.

00:26:13.890 --> 00:26:15.610
Where is Sae Bom?

00:26:15.610 --> 00:26:19.900
What? She's not in the building.

00:26:19.900 --> 00:26:22.840
The other detective and the girl are gone, too.

00:26:22.840 --> 00:26:25.070
They left, didn't they?

00:26:25.070 --> 00:26:27.630
The news said everything was fine outside.

00:26:27.630 --> 00:26:31.370
I heard martial law has been lifted except for the areas in lockdown.

00:26:32.080 --> 00:26:35.260
Maybe the door to the outside is open or something.

00:26:35.260 --> 00:26:37.240
I don't know what's going on outside, either.

00:26:37.240 --> 00:26:41.590
Oh, don't move! You have two gunshot wounds.

00:26:44.360 --> 00:26:46.860
I bit Andrew.

00:26:46.860 --> 00:26:49.580
What?

00:26:49.580 --> 00:26:53.360
He's a murderer and even more dangerous if he's infected.

00:26:53.360 --> 00:26:55.680
If he's alive,

00:26:57.300 --> 00:26:59.260
I have to catch him.

00:27:02.000 --> 00:27:03.670
Help him.

00:27:21.750 --> 00:27:23.980
What?

00:27:50.750 --> 00:27:55.590
Let's look for him on our way down before there are more victims.

00:27:55.590 --> 00:28:00.470
While the Central Disease Relief Center is minimizing the spread of infection with quick diagnosis and bold lockdowns,

00:28:00.470 --> 00:28:03.770
it looks like the prevention of Madness Rabies seems plausible.

00:28:03.770 --> 00:28:09.390
According to the insider, the current vaccine that's in clinical trials is showing a meaningful efficacy rate.

00:28:09.390 --> 00:28:13.060
And if positive results are produced, they will request immediate

00:28:13.060 --> 00:28:16.570
approval for usage with the Federal Health Department.

00:28:16.570 --> 00:28:21.030
- Drink some of this. You have to eat something to gain strength.
- Considering the danger of spreading the infection, the government decided to

00:28:21.030 --> 00:28:25.120
maintain the quarantine of the infected until the treatment therapy has been developed.

00:28:25.120 --> 00:28:28.400
Based on that, the nursing homes and apartments that are currently in lockdown

00:28:28.400 --> 00:28:30.910
will continue for now.

00:28:30.910 --> 00:28:33.710
And the residents in the region...

00:28:45.660 --> 00:28:49.350
Oh, look. The brave Detective is here.

00:28:49.350 --> 00:28:53.440
You must've gotten hurt in the electricity room.

00:28:53.440 --> 00:28:55.760
Are there people with injuries inside?

00:28:56.840 --> 00:28:59.070
The cleaner couple from the second floor.

00:28:59.070 --> 00:29:03.030
He got stabbed by Andrew, so I'm treating him on a humanitarian level.

00:29:03.030 --> 00:29:05.270
I don't see Andrew nor the building representative.

00:29:05.270 --> 00:29:06.620
Do you know where they are?

00:29:06.620 --> 00:29:09.060
They must have gone out.

00:29:12.110 --> 00:29:14.560
Where is your wife?

00:29:14.560 --> 00:29:16.820
Andrew is dangerous right now.

00:29:16.820 --> 00:29:19.090
Don't ever open the door for him.

00:29:19.090 --> 00:29:23.650
If possible, I'm thinking of bringing criminal charges against the three of you.

00:29:23.650 --> 00:29:26.190
The couple from across the hallway in unit 602...

00:29:26.190 --> 00:29:29.720
Sang Hee and that attorney fell for each other. Look at this.

00:29:29.720 --> 00:29:32.070
She did this to me.

00:29:32.070 --> 00:29:34.780
Shouldn't you catch them and lock them away first?

00:29:34.780 --> 00:29:37.430
We already stopped by unit 602.

00:29:37.430 --> 00:29:41.650
That attorney ahjussi showed us where you bit his arm.

00:29:42.450 --> 00:29:45.200
That's right. I'm infected,

00:29:45.200 --> 00:29:47.530
but there are so many people who have been infected.

00:29:47.530 --> 00:29:52.280
Do you think anyone will punish me for biting someone?

00:29:53.050 --> 00:29:54.960
Oh Joo Hyung.

00:29:56.660 --> 00:29:59.540
You're not infected.

00:30:00.790 --> 00:30:03.140
I know because I am.

00:30:04.220 --> 00:30:08.480
I'm barely holding back the urge to bite you.

00:30:08.480 --> 00:30:11.710
I took the pill, too. I took the pill, too!

00:30:11.710 --> 00:30:15.240
You don't always get infected by taking the pill.

00:30:15.240 --> 00:30:20.460
Some get infected much later, and some don't even get infected.

00:30:24.400 --> 00:30:26.710
Where is your husband?

00:30:32.670 --> 00:30:35.980
His condition keeps deteriorating. Is there anything you can do for him?

00:30:35.980 --> 00:30:38.610
Of course, his condition isn’t good

00:30:38.610 --> 00:30:40.810
when he has a knife stuck in his body.

00:30:40.810 --> 00:30:46.360
Honey, I’m okay. I’ll get up soon.

00:30:46.360 --> 00:30:50.060
So tell him to get out of here! Please!

00:30:50.060 --> 00:30:53.570
Ahjussi, this is my place!

00:31:09.320 --> 00:31:12.460
How long can he last?

00:31:12.460 --> 00:31:15.230
He’ll die right away if you pull out the knife,

00:31:15.230 --> 00:31:18.430
and if you leave it in, about two days or so?

00:31:19.290 --> 00:31:22.440
I’ll look for a way to get him out. Look after his wounds in the meantime.

00:31:22.440 --> 00:31:27.080
I gave him painkillers and even gave up my bedroom. What more do you want me to do?

00:31:33.350 --> 00:31:38.600
You're keeping them both here in case you get thirsty for blood, aren't you?

00:31:38.600 --> 00:31:41.240
Who do you think I am? What nonsense are you spewing?

00:31:41.240 --> 00:31:42.890
Have you been taking those pills?

00:31:42.890 --> 00:31:45.370
Is that why you thought you were infected?

00:31:52.560 --> 00:31:59.630
Yes, I was going to have them as my lunch! So what? I took the pills because I thought I might die!

00:31:59.630 --> 00:32:01.990
Just concentrate on treating him instead.

00:32:01.990 --> 00:32:04.700
If you create one more issue,

00:32:04.700 --> 00:32:07.480
I’ll lock you up in the basement.

00:32:07.480 --> 00:32:09.290
What proof do you have to lock me up?

00:32:09.290 --> 00:32:13.800
Are you the judge? Hey! Hey!

00:32:33.300 --> 00:32:37.220
Honey. This.

00:32:37.220 --> 00:32:39.150
Try this.

00:32:40.040 --> 00:32:43.970
If you take this pill, the wound is supposed to heal quickly.

00:32:50.860 --> 00:32:52.780
Did you drink?

00:32:58.050 --> 00:33:01.250
You do love me, don’t you?

00:33:01.250 --> 00:33:04.190
Don't bite me, even if you get infected.

00:33:16.440 --> 00:33:19.230
Sir, are you okay?

00:33:19.230 --> 00:33:23.580
Oh, of course, I am!

00:33:23.580 --> 00:33:28.060
You don’t look so well, either, though.

00:33:28.060 --> 00:33:32.470
- How is your wife doing?
- We’re fine,

00:33:32.470 --> 00:33:37.440
so please just take good care of my son.

00:33:38.260 --> 00:33:41.080
Isn’t Kim Dong Hyun back yet?

00:33:41.080 --> 00:33:46.740
What? Isn’t he on the 2nd floor?

00:33:48.330 --> 00:33:51.420
He did say he wanted to go out.

00:33:55.780 --> 00:34:02.060
If you happen to see him, please tell him to come home, since we’re okay.

00:34:02.060 --> 00:34:04.030
A home is...

00:34:04.030 --> 00:34:07.610
there for you to go to when things get hard.

00:34:08.350 --> 00:34:09.830
I understand.

00:34:09.830 --> 00:34:12.340
By chance, if Andrew…

00:34:14.250 --> 00:34:17.800
If you see an unfamiliar young guy, don’t ever open the door to him.

00:34:17.800 --> 00:34:20.010
He’s very dangerous.

00:34:21.040 --> 00:34:23.080
Oh, okay.

00:34:23.080 --> 00:34:25.720
But why would he come here?

00:34:25.720 --> 00:34:27.720
There are only two old folks living here.

00:34:27.720 --> 00:34:30.660
Sir, do you have enough food?

00:34:30.660 --> 00:34:33.230
Would you like us to bring you some more?

00:34:36.520 --> 00:34:40.280
Why would you offer him food when we don’t have enough for us?

00:34:40.280 --> 00:34:42.870
I’m going to give them some of mine!

00:34:42.870 --> 00:34:45.570
Why are you so selfish?

00:35:05.160 --> 00:35:07.370
The two of you, move aside.

00:35:07.370 --> 00:35:09.980
That guy is infected.

00:35:10.650 --> 00:35:13.760
I saw him biting Andrew.

00:35:13.760 --> 00:35:15.950
I’m infected, too.

00:35:15.950 --> 00:35:18.590
Let’s not fight, Building Representative.

00:35:18.590 --> 00:35:22.930
There’s a good chance Andrew is still in the building.

00:35:25.420 --> 00:35:28.220
Andrew is dead.

00:35:59.460 --> 00:36:04.940
I was going to go out and meet with the person in charge of the blockade, but the infected are right in front of the building.

00:36:04.940 --> 00:36:09.070
Still, we caught the murderer so all we have to do is wait quietly.

00:36:09.070 --> 00:36:13.920
Did you get rid of Andrew’s body then?

00:36:14.990 --> 00:36:17.100
It’s on the rooftop.

00:36:17.750 --> 00:36:20.860
You're the one who bit him and killed him!

00:36:21.470 --> 00:36:24.010
There’s no one on the rooftop.

00:36:26.620 --> 00:36:29.410
You must be trying to fool me,

00:36:29.410 --> 00:36:33.140
but do I look like an idiot? No way!

00:36:34.540 --> 00:36:39.010
I’m normal. I’m different from you infected people!

00:36:41.930 --> 00:36:45.000
It’s dangerous if you go alone, Building Representative.

00:36:49.110 --> 00:36:54.560
Is it okay to leave that ahjumma alone?

00:36:54.560 --> 00:36:57.210
She lost her family.

00:36:59.240 --> 00:37:01.750
I’m sure she needs someone to hate.

00:37:03.930 --> 00:37:06.230
Oh, my head hurts...

00:37:41.880 --> 00:37:45.850
The police bastard hid Andrew’s body. He's lying to me.

00:37:45.850 --> 00:37:48.770
I'll just kill him if I have to.

00:37:53.910 --> 00:37:57.890
Andrew and Kim Dong Hyun must both have left.

00:38:04.730 --> 00:38:06.220
What?

00:38:09.730 --> 00:38:11.210
Wait...

00:38:21.710 --> 00:38:26.060
Oh, don’t do that! What if the infected get in?

00:38:26.060 --> 00:38:27.910
Don’t come out.

00:38:58.080 --> 00:38:59.880
Are you okay?

00:39:06.650 --> 00:39:08.960
How long has it been since you got bit?

00:39:15.420 --> 00:39:19.150
Hey, isn’t that the jobless guy from the 3rd floor?

00:39:19.760 --> 00:39:21.380
It looks like he got hurt.

00:39:21.380 --> 00:39:24.500
Hurt? He got bit!

00:39:34.250 --> 00:39:37.250
Well, um...

00:39:37.990 --> 00:39:41.360
isn't he infected?

00:39:42.080 --> 00:39:44.470
He hasn't had an episode yet.

00:39:45.150 --> 00:39:49.340
If he stays with his family, he might be able to endure better.

00:40:16.330 --> 00:40:20.200
Dad, I'm sorry.

00:40:22.820 --> 00:40:24.760
Oh no...

00:40:30.090 --> 00:40:33.080
Honey!

00:40:33.080 --> 00:40:36.450
Dong Hyun is back!

00:40:56.930 --> 00:40:59.560
Moon Hee.

00:40:59.560 --> 00:41:01.120
Yes?

00:41:02.910 --> 00:41:06.200
Are you okay? Do you feel better?

00:41:06.200 --> 00:41:08.230
It hurts less.

00:41:08.230 --> 00:41:10.750
Who gave you those pills?

00:41:13.250 --> 00:41:18.180
Should I… try taking the knife out?

00:41:24.260 --> 00:41:26.180
Hold on.

00:41:28.230 --> 00:41:30.190
Do you have more pills?

00:41:36.180 --> 00:41:38.210
Give me the water.

00:41:45.080 --> 00:41:47.250
Let’s try removing it.

00:41:48.440 --> 00:41:50.530
I’m going to pull it out.

00:41:50.530 --> 00:41:52.930
Moon Hee, you know…

00:41:53.700 --> 00:41:56.970
I don’t think I can leave empty-handed after ending up like this.

00:41:58.990 --> 00:42:01.170
Let’s take this apartment.

00:42:04.220 --> 00:42:06.160
How?

00:42:20.940 --> 00:42:22.860
Sir…

00:42:22.860 --> 00:42:26.370
What is it? Is he dead?

00:42:27.820 --> 00:42:30.490
I pulled out the knife.

00:42:30.490 --> 00:42:34.240
I told you not to! Did he bleed all over the floor?

00:42:34.240 --> 00:42:37.230
Why don’t you people listen?

00:42:40.710 --> 00:42:45.420
Sir. You don’t have any family, right?

00:42:54.800 --> 00:42:57.330
Aigoo,

00:42:57.330 --> 00:43:00.190
doesn’t it look more swollen than before?

00:43:00.190 --> 00:43:04.250
Oppa, how many times do I have to tell you no?

00:43:05.360 --> 00:43:07.810
Are you sure?

00:43:07.810 --> 00:43:09.220
I already told you!

00:43:09.220 --> 00:43:12.810
Stop touching it! That’s why it’s getting more swollen!

00:43:15.010 --> 00:43:17.690
You really think I’m fine, right?

00:43:19.400 --> 00:43:21.210
What do we do about the bitcoin?

00:43:21.210 --> 00:43:24.630
I have the passcode but not the laptop.

00:43:26.720 --> 00:43:29.210
The laptop!

00:43:32.430 --> 00:43:36.170
Sang Hee! I’ll give you the money, so open the door!

00:43:36.170 --> 00:43:38.340
Sang Hee! Open the door!

00:43:38.340 --> 00:43:40.960
- Sang Hee!
- Maybe he’s doing that so he can bite us.

00:43:40.960 --> 00:43:43.630
I’ll give you the money!

00:43:46.940 --> 00:43:48.510
How much?

00:43:48.510 --> 00:43:52.740
Hey, that cleaner bastard has totally gone nuts!

00:43:53.630 --> 00:43:55.590
Get away!

00:44:02.680 --> 00:44:05.600
If Go Se Gyoo’s condition becomes critical, we’ll have to get him out somehow.

00:44:05.600 --> 00:44:07.190
We can't leave him to die.

00:44:07.190 --> 00:44:09.500
Detective Jung!

00:44:14.600 --> 00:44:18.350
Detective Jung, help me! I almost died.

00:44:19.160 --> 00:44:21.750
What is it now?

00:44:21.750 --> 00:44:25.420
He gave us the pills. He said the wound will heal if he takes it.

00:44:25.420 --> 00:44:28.960
Are you nuts? That's not true. I'm not crazy!

00:44:28.960 --> 00:44:31.350
Why would I increase the number of monsters?

00:44:32.610 --> 00:44:34.180
Is your husband okay?

00:44:34.180 --> 00:44:37.910
He's still struggling. He's lying down right now.

00:44:37.910 --> 00:44:40.860
Can't you kick that man out somewhere?

00:44:40.860 --> 00:44:43.570
I'm too scared to have him in here with us.

00:44:43.570 --> 00:44:46.680
You have to kick these people out if anything!

00:44:46.680 --> 00:44:51.440
Why don't you believe me? We're both residents of this building!

00:44:51.440 --> 00:44:56.240
It's the first time hearing you say that we're both residents of this building.

00:44:56.240 --> 00:44:58.350
I warned you, didn't I?

00:44:58.350 --> 00:44:59.710
Let's go to the gym.

00:44:59.710 --> 00:45:03.210
My laptop, laptop. Tell them to give me my laptop.

00:45:03.210 --> 00:45:06.690
Laptop! My laptop!

00:45:16.440 --> 00:45:18.980
Are you happy that I'm leaving?

00:45:31.610 --> 00:45:36.040
What are you doing right now? Where are you taking the doctor?

00:45:36.040 --> 00:45:38.200
I'm planning to quarantine him.

00:45:38.200 --> 00:45:42.500
Watch yourself if you don't want to end up like this, too.

00:45:56.690 --> 00:46:00.460
Honey, all this is ours, right?

00:46:00.460 --> 00:46:04.900
Of course. You said that bastard doesn't have any family.

00:46:04.900 --> 00:46:07.600
He nearly killed me.

00:46:07.600 --> 00:46:11.990
We can ask him to compensate us for damages with this apartment.

00:46:11.990 --> 00:46:14.540
He'd never agree to it.

00:46:14.540 --> 00:46:20.420
We can get rid of him before the lockdown lifts. They'll think one of the infected killed him.

00:46:20.420 --> 00:46:22.180
Right?

00:46:23.730 --> 00:46:26.940
Oh, Moon Hee... Moon Hee...

00:46:27.930 --> 00:46:30.190
- Get me some water.
- Oh, okay.

00:46:45.320 --> 00:46:47.750
Just take this, too.

00:46:50.760 --> 00:46:53.400
I'm thirsty for some strange reason.

00:47:06.180 --> 00:47:08.450
How many are there?

00:47:08.450 --> 00:47:10.340
One,

00:47:11.450 --> 00:47:13.360
two,

00:47:14.160 --> 00:47:16.040
three...

00:47:28.380 --> 00:47:32.830
Why didn't you leave with your wife?

00:47:37.610 --> 00:47:40.960
I have to watch the house until she comes back.

00:47:40.960 --> 00:47:46.420
It took a lot of effort to get this place through special provisions for civil servants.

00:47:51.220 --> 00:47:55.710
I know that you were worried about us, too.

00:47:55.710 --> 00:48:01.630
If you hadn't stayed behind, something bad would have happened.

00:48:02.650 --> 00:48:04.880
Thank you.

00:48:09.660 --> 00:48:13.810
I'll get some rest and then look for Andrew one more time.

00:48:13.810 --> 00:48:16.950
It could be dangerous, so both of you should go home.

00:48:16.950 --> 00:48:19.870
We can help.

00:48:19.870 --> 00:48:22.670
I could be dangerous to you, too.

00:48:23.860 --> 00:48:30.580
Your brother seems to have gotten a lot better, but not me.

00:48:32.400 --> 00:48:34.030
Hey...

00:48:36.940 --> 00:48:39.170
Be safe.

00:49:34.680 --> 00:49:36.520
Bom.

00:49:40.300 --> 00:49:42.210
Are you well?

00:49:55.370 --> 00:49:57.470
I miss you.

00:50:24.100 --> 00:50:27.060
We survived thanks to Jung Yi Hyun.

00:50:27.060 --> 00:50:29.720
He is infected, but—

00:50:29.720 --> 00:50:32.350
Then he's home, right?

00:50:32.350 --> 00:50:35.170
It's dangerous, so don't go outside and stay home!

00:50:35.170 --> 00:50:36.680
The lockdown will lift soon!

00:50:36.680 --> 00:50:38.320
What? Really?

00:50:38.320 --> 00:50:41.150
See? She says not to go outside!

00:50:42.000 --> 00:50:43.580
Hey, that's amazing.

00:50:59.510 --> 00:51:04.400
Hey! Sang Hee. I knew you would come!

00:51:05.660 --> 00:51:07.390
Let go.

00:51:07.390 --> 00:51:10.080
Let go and talk.

00:51:10.080 --> 00:51:12.930
What can you do without a key?

00:51:12.930 --> 00:51:15.830
Building Representative, please help me.

00:51:15.830 --> 00:51:18.230
I only came to help him.

00:51:18.230 --> 00:51:20.760
You must be crazy!

00:51:24.940 --> 00:51:28.850
Wouldn't it be better for us to get rid of that detective bastard?

00:51:28.850 --> 00:51:32.740
His wife ran away, so we just need to get rid of that bastard.

00:51:33.980 --> 00:51:38.380
Do you want us to kill a detective?

00:51:38.380 --> 00:51:41.010
He's infected.

00:51:42.650 --> 00:51:48.040
I'll break that for you with this, so do as I tell you.

00:52:03.320 --> 00:52:05.940
Help me!

00:52:18.840 --> 00:52:21.000
Oh Joo Hyung.

00:52:21.000 --> 00:52:24.910
Calm down, and let go of her.

00:52:24.910 --> 00:52:30.370
Jung Yi Hyun, let's kill all the uninfected people

00:52:30.370 --> 00:52:33.440
and say that everything happened because of the disease.

00:52:33.440 --> 00:52:38.880
That's right. The monsters did everything.

00:52:38.880 --> 00:52:43.250
You guys are the monsters, not the infected people!

00:52:43.250 --> 00:52:45.430
Aren't you thirsty?

00:52:58.730 --> 00:53:01.920
Should we find out who the real monster is?

00:53:20.650 --> 00:53:23.960
Jung Yi Hyun! Jung Yi Hyun!

00:53:23.960 --> 00:53:25.520
Don't you love the smell of blood?

00:53:25.520 --> 00:53:28.360
Don't hold it in! You must have lived your whole life holding it in!

00:53:28.360 --> 00:53:31.860
Jung Yi Hyun! Jung Yi Hyun!

00:53:31.860 --> 00:53:34.060
Come out! Come out!

00:53:34.060 --> 00:53:36.600
Come out!

00:53:36.600 --> 00:53:38.620
Come out!

00:53:42.340 --> 00:53:44.790
Why won't everyone listen to me?

00:53:44.790 --> 00:53:48.460
This is my building. Listen to me!

00:53:53.560 --> 00:53:57.350
Calm down! I'm not here to arrest you!

00:54:01.210 --> 00:54:03.880
You killed my husband.

00:54:03.880 --> 00:54:06.560
I even captured a murderer, and I'm not infected, either.

00:54:06.560 --> 00:54:08.220
I'm qualified to be Resident Representative.

00:54:08.220 --> 00:54:13.290
Okay. When you're released from jail, I'll vote for you.

00:54:14.180 --> 00:54:16.250
- Okay.
- Come out, come out!

00:54:16.250 --> 00:54:18.670
Come out!

00:54:18.670 --> 00:54:22.270
Just come, bite me and change!

00:54:22.270 --> 00:54:25.350
I'll have an episode soon, too!

00:54:26.860 --> 00:54:28.710
You're dead.

00:54:50.440 --> 00:54:52.300
Hyun...

00:54:58.350 --> 00:55:00.360
I'm here.

00:55:16.910 --> 00:55:19.440
I realized it when I heard what you said.

00:55:20.320 --> 00:55:26.840
What matters in a home is who you are with.

00:55:29.840 --> 00:55:33.860
I plan to be with you in the future.

00:55:37.700 --> 00:55:40.270
Stay with me.

00:56:19.680 --> 00:56:24.480
I don't care what state you're in.

00:57:37.010 --> 00:57:40.660
Are you sure there is an antibody carrier inside the apartment building?

00:57:40.660 --> 00:57:42.240
There was a testimony.

00:57:42.240 --> 00:57:46.250
Please tell me everything you know about the infected.

00:57:46.250 --> 00:57:49.210
We may need the information to develop a treatment.

00:57:49.210 --> 00:57:51.960
There's not much that I know,

00:57:51.960 --> 00:57:56.900
but Na Hyun Kyung said that her brother's wound stayed the same.

00:57:56.900 --> 00:57:59.780
That it didn't get worse or better.

00:57:59.780 --> 00:58:02.920
Did you ask for full authority solely based on that?

00:58:02.920 --> 00:58:04.750
Ji Soo.

00:58:06.390 --> 00:58:09.440
Did we ever have anything we can rely on?

00:58:29.650 --> 00:58:34.900
Oppa, open the door, please. I got the bitcoins!

00:58:34.900 --> 00:58:37.080
It has been tough, hasn't it?

00:58:37.080 --> 00:58:40.220
I'm sorry that I've been so sensitive.
[So Yoon, did you make it out okay? I'm sorry. I realized how precious you are to me, now that you're gone...]

00:58:40.220 --> 00:58:44.820
I mean, we did all that to be happy.
[So Yoon, did you make it out okay? I'm sorry. I realized how precious you are to me, now that you're gone...]

00:58:44.820 --> 00:58:45.780
[To Sin So Yoon: So Yoon, did you make it out okay? I'm sorry. I realized how precious you are to me, now that you're gone...]

00:58:45.780 --> 00:58:48.520
Oppa, are you listening to me? Oppa!

00:58:48.520 --> 00:58:51.110
[Sin So Yoon]

00:58:51.110 --> 00:58:53.010
Oppa! Oppa Hae Sung!

00:58:53.010 --> 00:58:55.680
Honey! I'm telling you, we can be happy now!

00:58:55.680 --> 00:58:59.010
- Open the door!
- So-So Yoon? So Yoon...

00:58:59.010 --> 00:59:02.770
- I'm really sorry. It's all my fault. Please?
- Oppa!

00:59:02.770 --> 00:59:04.390
Don't ever call me again.

00:59:04.390 --> 00:59:06.130
- No, no, no, I...
- Oppa...

00:59:06.130 --> 00:59:07.620
You're in there, right?

00:59:07.620 --> 00:59:11.410
I've been repenting. Honestly.

00:59:11.410 --> 00:59:12.930
Can you hear me?

00:59:12.930 --> 00:59:14.690
- So–
- Open the door for a second.

00:59:14.690 --> 00:59:17.080
Gosh, but I really have been repenting.

00:59:17.080 --> 00:59:21.270
I'm telling you, we can be happy now. Oppa?

00:59:21.270 --> 00:59:24.910
- The call is not going through...
- Geez...

00:59:30.210 --> 00:59:35.480
We were happy together. We can be even happier.

00:59:37.020 --> 00:59:41.300
Open the door. Please? Open it.

00:59:42.370 --> 00:59:44.970
Fine. I'll have to take the next best thing.

00:59:48.380 --> 00:59:50.550
Did he bite your arm?

00:59:52.600 --> 00:59:55.460
[Sin So Yoon]

00:59:55.460 --> 00:59:58.310
Is the internet working now?

00:59:58.310 --> 01:00:01.990
Oppa, I'll give you some coins.

01:00:01.990 --> 01:00:03.990
- The passcode.
- Oh, okay...

01:00:12.720 --> 01:00:16.620
[OPbit]

