- compared to three months ago, 97.5%...
- What...

01:01:19.380 --> 01:01:21.600
Oh, my God! Aigoo!

01:01:23.230 --> 01:01:24.490
H-Hey...

01:01:24.490 --> 01:01:28.010
Mom, they're here. We'll live now!

01:01:28.010 --> 01:01:30.380
- I was right!
- Aigoo!

01:01:30.380 --> 01:01:33.580
I told you they would come! I told you so!

01:01:33.580 --> 01:01:36.580
- Aigoo!
- Be gentle...

01:01:36.580 --> 01:01:38.520
Aigoo!

01:01:38.520 --> 01:01:40.720
Take it.

01:01:40.720 --> 01:01:42.740
Thank you!

01:01:49.710 --> 01:01:51.880
No, I never bit anyone.

01:01:51.880 --> 01:01:53.120
I'm telling you the truth.

01:01:53.120 --> 01:01:55.440
I'm not thirsty, either.

01:01:55.440 --> 01:01:58.500
Try giving me some water. It's true. I don't get thirsty.

01:01:58.500 --> 01:02:00.970
It's true. I never bit anyone.

01:02:00.970 --> 01:02:04.220
He has been perfectly fine. He could have recovered completely.

01:02:04.220 --> 01:02:06.370
I think he's actually recovered. Right, Oppa, you're all better now, right?

01:02:06.370 --> 01:02:09.630
Yes, since I'm not thirsty.

01:02:17.840 --> 01:02:20.460
Nothing's wrong with him, right? He's fine, isn't he?

01:02:21.250 --> 01:02:22.950
- I don't get thirsty.
- Don't talk too much!

01:02:22.950 --> 01:02:25.780
Yes, I'm being honest!

01:02:29.730 --> 01:02:32.910
We found the antibody carrier. We're returning now.

01:02:34.560 --> 01:02:38.510
I'll take care of Yoon Sae Bom.

01:02:38.510 --> 01:02:42.230
Do what you need to do. Just bring in the antibody carrier.

01:02:44.280 --> 01:02:46.800
Be careful with him.

01:02:46.800 --> 01:02:52.330
Take Yoon Sae Bom and Jung Yi Hyun to the dorm.

01:02:52.330 --> 01:02:53.870
Yes, Sir.

01:02:53.870 --> 01:02:55.910
No! No!

01:02:55.910 --> 01:02:57.860
This is our home! What are you doing?

01:02:57.860 --> 01:02:59.760
No! No!

01:02:59.760 --> 01:03:02.740
Honey! Look at this! No! It's our apartment!

01:03:02.740 --> 01:03:04.460
No, it's our apartment!

01:03:04.460 --> 01:03:07.040
No! No!

01:03:09.090 --> 01:03:11.140
No!

01:03:12.110 --> 01:03:13.740
This is our home!

01:03:13.740 --> 01:03:15.270
- No!
- It's mine!

01:03:15.270 --> 01:03:17.190
- This is our apartment!
- Let go! It's mine!

01:03:17.190 --> 01:03:18.830
This is our place! Let go!

01:03:18.830 --> 01:03:20.630
No! This is ours!

01:03:20.630 --> 01:03:23.980
It's ours! Let go of me!

01:03:23.980 --> 01:03:25.750
- I'm going to take it with me!
- It's ours!

01:03:25.750 --> 01:03:28.380
- I said it's mine!
- This is our home!

01:03:31.020 --> 01:03:34.850
Just stay here. It's too bad if it's hot.

01:03:34.850 --> 01:03:39.430
Don't you dare think this is the end! Remember!

01:03:39.430 --> 01:03:44.070
Sae Bom, you'll vote for me, right?

01:03:44.070 --> 01:03:46.940
Sure. Let's go.

01:04:02.450 --> 01:04:07.660
We shouldn't leave Kim Se Hoon here, right?

01:04:08.660 --> 01:04:11.060
Let's move him to his place.

01:04:11.060 --> 01:04:13.230
I'll go open the door.

01:04:43.690 --> 01:04:46.300
Call Yoon Sae Bom here.

01:05:11.760 --> 01:05:13.990
Drop the gun, Yoon Sae Bom.

01:05:13.990 --> 01:05:17.620
Just shoot him. I can take a hit.

01:05:20.680 --> 01:05:22.810
Drop the gun if you want him to live!

01:05:22.810 --> 01:05:25.340
Never. Just shoot him now!

01:05:54.710 --> 01:05:57.480
It's fresh blood.

01:06:41.350 --> 01:06:44.360
Yi Hyun.

01:06:44.360 --> 01:06:46.890
Yi Hyun.

01:06:46.890 --> 01:06:50.650
♫ When cruel days come to me ♫

01:06:50.650 --> 01:06:53.210
♫ The deepening sound of breathing ♫

01:06:53.210 --> 01:06:55.250
I...

01:06:55.250 --> 01:06:58.680
told you that I was going to be the bad cop.

01:06:58.680 --> 01:07:01.170
You...

01:07:01.170 --> 01:07:02.600
keep being the good cop.

01:07:02.600 --> 01:07:07.070
♫ With cutting words ♫

01:07:07.070 --> 01:07:10.460
Hey!

01:07:10.460 --> 01:07:13.530
♫ Take me, I'm exhausted ♫

01:07:13.530 --> 01:07:15.690
♫ Burning through the grayish light ♫

01:07:15.690 --> 01:07:19.570
♫ Hold on to me, I'm stained in red ♫

01:07:19.570 --> 01:07:23.400
Yi Hyun! No. You can't!

01:07:23.400 --> 01:07:25.270
Yi Hyun!

01:07:25.270 --> 01:07:30.010
No. Yi Hyun!

01:07:54.770 --> 01:07:56.880
Look at them.

01:08:06.960 --> 01:08:11.150
♫ Remember the moments we had on the beautiful hills ♫

01:08:11.150 --> 01:08:14.280
♫ Near where we used to live ♫

01:08:20.010 --> 01:08:23.970
♫ We would just lie on the ground, feel the warm sunshine ♫

01:08:23.970 --> 01:08:27.340
♫ And just forget the world ♫

01:08:32.870 --> 01:08:37.800
♫ It feels like I had a dream, a dream that I can ♫

01:08:37.800 --> 01:08:40.940
♫ Have again ♫

01:08:42.370 --> 01:08:43.980
Mr. Lee Seung Young.

01:08:43.980 --> 01:08:47.320
♫ 'Cause I can see nothing like that here ♫

01:08:47.320 --> 01:08:51.890
♫ Where I am, where I am now ♫

01:08:56.430 --> 01:08:59.820
♫ Is this the end ♫

01:09:02.870 --> 01:09:05.410
♫ Is this the end ♫

01:09:05.410 --> 01:09:09.520
♫ I know, I know ♫

01:09:09.520 --> 01:09:13.070
♫ You don't need to answer ♫

01:09:19.180 --> 01:09:21.500
♫ I know it is the end ♫

01:09:21.500 --> 01:09:23.070
Be careful.

01:09:23.070 --> 01:09:25.610
Aren't you tired after all that running?

01:09:25.610 --> 01:09:28.330
- I'm not tired at all.
- Really?

01:09:28.330 --> 01:09:30.930
Then shall we take it up a notch?

01:09:30.930 --> 01:09:32.100
How about the gym?

01:09:32.100 --> 01:09:34.800
All the residents can use the facility now.

01:09:38.690 --> 01:09:42.670
- I have plans, so I have to go back home.
- What?

01:09:42.670 --> 01:09:43.940
Bye!

01:09:43.940 --> 01:09:45.960
Which plans?

01:09:45.960 --> 01:09:47.590
Seo Yoon.

01:09:47.590 --> 01:09:50.800
All right. Shall we go then?

01:09:58.630 --> 01:10:00.720
What are you thinking?

01:10:00.720 --> 01:10:05.440
Last year when we were locked up here.

01:10:05.440 --> 01:10:07.640
It was tough, wasn't it?

01:10:07.640 --> 01:10:09.570
A little.

01:10:10.330 --> 01:10:13.010
But it was okay because you were with me.

01:10:17.020 --> 01:10:20.360
When did you start liking me?

01:10:20.360 --> 01:10:24.080
Since the beginning, I told you. Why don't you believe me?

01:10:24.080 --> 01:10:27.940
I said to myself that you were my destiny, that I'll be with you forever.

01:10:27.940 --> 01:10:31.510
So you never gave up?

01:10:31.510 --> 01:10:33.100
Why do you think I became a cop?

01:10:33.100 --> 01:10:36.880
Hey! Don't tell me you became a cop because of me!

01:10:36.880 --> 01:10:41.060
I thought about going to the States, but I couldn't stop thinking about what you said.

01:10:41.060 --> 01:10:45.520
You said our future was full of choices, so I should do whatever I wanted. But then you went with the SOU!

01:10:45.520 --> 01:10:48.430
Hey, I had no idea.

01:10:50.860 --> 01:10:54.390
So are you happy now?

01:10:56.580 --> 01:11:00.620
Of course. Only when I'm with you.

01:11:02.250 --> 01:11:03.690
I'm not that happy otherwise.

01:11:03.690 --> 01:11:05.600
Stop lying.

01:11:06.870 --> 01:11:10.210
The first one home will be exempt from recycling duty for a week!

01:11:10.210 --> 01:11:11.820
You're cheating! Hey!

01:11:11.820 --> 01:11:13.630
Including the food garbage!

01:11:13.630 --> 01:11:14.940
I refuse to lose!

01:11:14.940 --> 01:11:16.340
♫ Realize ♫

